reviews.text: Just great sushi .. if your phone cannot access app. They loan you one ... And the delivery system is just so futuristic ...
All sushi falls apart when you try to pick them up, rice was a bit on the hard side. Is a bit on the pricey side for the quality of food you are getting

Good shushi, good service and excellent prices

I loved the concept of ordering from the phone. The food was served on a train-like track. The plates of sushi and sashimi would show up on the side of the table via the train track and that was cool.

result.name: 元気寿司

reviews.text: 跟同樣價位的壽司店相比，無論是米的質量還是海產的新鮮度都有凸出的表現。
Netter Sushi Laden mit einiger Auswahl. Die Gerichte kommen mit einer kleinen Bahn angefahren. Die Gerichte sind recht günstig und alles frisch zubereitet. Für eine kleinen Happen zwischendurch.
Just great sushi .. if your phone cannot access app. They loan you one ... And the delivery system is just so futuristic ...

Kolejna miejscowka porzadnej sieci z sushi. Ceny jak wszedzie. Zamiast na tablecie, zamawia sie na wlasnym telefonie poprzez pobranie dedykowanej dla siebie wersji aplikacji. Czasem to nie dziala, wtedy daja standartowego tableta do zamawiania. 
Obsluga sprawna, jedzenie dobre.
這裏的環境舒服及乾淨, 食物整體不錯,  另有架電子傳遞食物嘅車仔,最吸引小朋友去食㗎喇！
